### Get Service DNS Name


{{< example csharp >}}

```csharp
using Pulumi;
using Aws = Pulumi.Aws;

class MyStack : Stack
{
    public MyStack()
    {
        var current = Output.Create(Aws.GetRegion.InvokeAsync());
        var test = current.Apply(current => Output.Create(Aws.GetService.InvokeAsync(new Aws.GetServiceArgs
        {
            Region = current.Name,
            ServiceId = "ec2",
        })));
    }

}
```
